  "logNo": "110165792418",
  "title": "한화리조트&딸기농장체험",
  "addDate": "2013. 4. 8.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110165792418",
  "html_size": 190227,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110165792418\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110165792418\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>토요일. </p>\r\n<p>돌풍을 동반한 비가 내렸네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그 비를 뚫고 양평한화리조트에 갔습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>친구 여럿과 함께 가족동반 여행을 했거든요. </p>\r\n<p>워크샵으로 진행된거지만</p>\r\n<p>실제.</p>\r\n<p>그냥 가족동반 여행이나 다름없죠 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c99cfc7dceee9aeb.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130408_4/isuhani_1365402045970jyJom_JPEG/IMG_0707.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c99cfc7dceee9aeb.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>진료마치고 가서</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>제일 늦게 도착했습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>부랴부랴 챙겨서 가느라 내복위에 겉옷만 입혔네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>미안하다 딸아 ㅜ.ㅠ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>여기는 양평한화리조트 내에 있는 바베큐 식당. '님프가든'</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130408_213/isuhani_1365402046230CrbwR_JPEG/IMG_0732.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_213/isuhani_1365402046230CrbwR_JPEG/IMG_0732.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130408_213/isuhani_1365402046230CrbwR_JPEG/IMG_0732.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>식사 후에</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>양평한화리조트 1층에 있는 세미나실에서 워크샵을 진행합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들을 위한 별도의 프로그램이 준비되어있어서</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들이 호기심어린 눈으로 프로그램을 기다립니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130408_22/isuhani_1365402046597ykmud_JPEG/IMG_0778.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_22/isuhani_1365402046597ykmud_JPEG/IMG_0778.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130408_22/isuhani_1365402046597ykmud_JPEG/IMG_0778.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>바닥에 앉아서 그림을 그리기도 하고. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc6de5148005d7d4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_299/isuhani_1365402046822kzHJR_JPEG/IMG_0812.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc6de5148005d7d4.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>친구, 동생, 오빠 들과 어울려 놀기도 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들은 여럿이 어울려서 재밌는지 늦게까지 잠들지 않더군요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>어른들은 애들을 재우고 나서도 한참을 더 즐깁니다. ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>양평에는 새벽에 눈이 많이 내리더군요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/38e96eafe2917901.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_174/isuhani_1365402046996vwEsz_JPEG/IMG_0898.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/38e96eafe2917901.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>다음날. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>양수리 딸기체험농장을 찾아갑니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>양수리의 두물머리... 음.. 양수리나 두물머리나 같은 말이죠?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두물머리 가는 길에 딸기체험농장이 있어요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두물머리를 그렇게 많이 다녔는데도, 딸기체험농장이 있는건 처음알았습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>양수리는 도로와 여러곳을 보수공사해서 예전보다 많이 깨끗해졌더군요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>농장 주변은 흙밭인데, 비가 온 뒤라 질퍽질퍽...&nbsp; ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>체험시작 전에 </p>\r\n<p>모여앉아서 기다리는 중.</p>\r\n<p>농장주 아저씨가 딸기에 대해 설명을 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/80c1a9f6266f3dba.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_150/isuhani_13654020471439PjCs_JPEG/IMG_0906.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/80c1a9f6266f3dba.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>설명이 귀에 들어올리가 없죠?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>신났습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/25372d1e64923475.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130408_130/isuhani_1365402138790t5X7I_JPEG/IMG_0923.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/25372d1e64923475.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>밀짚모자 쓴 아저씨를 따라가면 딸기 하우스가 나온다는군요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>여러 일행들이 같이 모여서 출발을 기다립니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f7e77e1d4fdb797e.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_219/isuhani_1365402138931DM4s4_JPEG/IMG_0927.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f7e77e1d4fdb797e.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>비닐하우스가 24개동 정도 된다는데,</p>\r\n<p>저희가 체험하는 비닐하우스는 멀리 있더군요. </p>\r\n<p>한참을 걸어갔습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d97a91b057677df2.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130408_45/isuhani_1365402139100t85Fv_JPEG/IMG_0929.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d97a91b057677df2.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>하우스 안은 이렇게 생겼네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>고랑을 따라 죽 걸으면서</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>맘에 드는 딸기를 따서 플라스틱 팩을 가득 채우면 됩니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>안에서 따서 먹으면 안된다고 밀짚모자 아저씨가 계속 주의를 주더군요..</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f89cc4b22c2eecc6.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_47/isuhani_1365402139281H81Co_JPEG/IMG_0932.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f89cc4b22c2eecc6.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>둘째는 조심조심... </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이쁜거, 큰거, 맛있어보이는거.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>골라서 땁니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e05e4c5d538fa8a3.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130408_83/isuhani_1365402139514MOWcf_JPEG/IMG_0935.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e05e4c5d538fa8a3.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>딸기 많~ 이 따자요~!!! </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>응. 많이 따렴.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c3f6c0f19eea2a5e.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_248/isuhani_1365402139663y8tyV_JPEG/IMG_0939.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c3f6c0f19eea2a5e.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>오늘 딸기체험의 결과물</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>시중에서 사 먹는 딸기보다 달고 맛있더라구요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/af9dcfc499326215.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_228/isuhani_13654021398580haQn_JPEG/IMG_0964.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/af9dcfc499326215.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>돌아가는길 역시 멀어요 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들끼리 어울려서 장난치고 달리기하고.. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>재밌어 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e5d92c04848b5d34.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_188/isuhani_1365402140099paSXW_JPEG/IMG_0971.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e5d92c04848b5d34.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>힘들었으니까.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>밥 많이 먹는다고..</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>커다란 밥 그릇 하나를 자기가 가지고서 열심히 먹습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>여기는 남양주시 조안면 능내리의 시골밥상.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0ce22e5bc425cb60.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130408_172/isuhani_1365402140592T5jcw_JPEG/IMG_0981.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66496A2')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0ce22e5bc425cb60.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>돌아오는 차 안에서 가족들은 모두 잠이 듭니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>집에도착해서도 한참을 더 잔 애들은</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>또 밤늦게까지 잠을 안자고 버팁니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그래도</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이쁘다고 사진 찍어주고 있는 아빠. ^^;;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>주말. </p>\r\n<p>알차게 잘 보냈네요~</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
